Jean-Paul L. Montupet



Mr. Jean-Paul L. Montupet is on the Board of Directors at IHS, Inc., Assurant, Inc., WABCO Europe BVBA, WABCO Holdings, Inc., Lexmark International, Inc., National Electrical Manufacturers Association, St. Louis Public Library Foundation and Winston Churchill Memorial & Library. Mr. Montupet was previously employed as Non-Executive Chairman by PartnerRe Ltd., President by Emerson Europe SA, Executive Vice President by Emerson Electric Co., Chief Executive Officer by Emerson Electric Asia Pacific Ltd., and Chairman-North American Operations by Moteurs Leroy-Somer SA. He also served on the board at Leroy-Somer SA and National Electrical Manufacturers Association. He received his MBA from École des Hautes Études Commerciales de Paris.



